data.description: Welcome to your updated 3bds 1.5ba home. This charming residence offers a spacious open concept floor plan ready to make memories. The kitchen boasts modern finishes and fresh cabinetry, subway backsplash and moderns appliances. The primary bedroom features a modern en suite bath with striking flooring. The backyard patio is perfect for entertaining and relaxation with family and friends. This large lot provides plenty space for gardening or play. Shed is freshly painted ready to be use as a workshop or storage space. Elementary school is right behind this charming home. Enjoy the friendly neighborhood and all this home has to offer! Washer and Dryer included! UPGRADES: Roof (1yr old) Back Yard Patio Freshly painted, new siding, new roof and well maintained shed. INCLUDES: Washer and Dryer Front Door Key Pad TV Wall Mounts Stove Outdoor lights There is a Bluetooth doorbell that plugs into the wall inside that will stay.
